```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant F as frontend app
  participant FP as frontend sidecar
  participant BP as backend sidecar
  participant B as backend app

  F->>FP: HTTP request to backend DNS
  FP->>FP: policy (timeouts/retries) + load balance
  FP->>BP: mTLS connection + request
  BP->>B: forward over localhost
  B-->>BP: response
  BP-->>FP: response
  FP-->>F: response
```
